name: DPC 2023 SA Spring Tour Division I – presented by ESB Liga Esports
description: Welcome to the DPC 2023 SA Tour 2 ESB Liga Esports Betsafe  Division I! We have the best 8 teams of the region, where they will be facing each other to reach the top 2 positions and win the spot to the Berlin Major of the Tour 2, in addition to accumulating the highest amount of DPC Points and be closer to The International.
